{
  "stem": "3277.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It took us maybe two, three months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It came a verdict, you know, from Moscow or from where.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Those people who said they are communist, they gave them a-- a verdict for-- for 10 years to-- to serve in those-- in those camps.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those who said they belong-- belonged to the Socialist Party, they used to get five years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And those who-- like myself who said they not belong to any party, three years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They called them social [NON-ENGLISH], which means very dangerous element.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this went through, we used-- people used to die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what-- and dying was this-- it started with the legs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They used to get swollen legs because of-- of the no-- no nutrition, nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And soon-- and at-- at-- even if you used to talk to that guy, everything was OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As soon the swelling came through the body, without no pain, they died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the morning, used to try to wake him up, nobody to talk to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was dead.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then we used to have a big problem to bury.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was-- the-- the-- the ground was ice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then we could dig, let's say, five, 10 inches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we used to put down woods.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They used to burn for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The next day, we could dig another 10 inches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And as soon we got about, let's say, over a-- a foot and a half, we would put that guy into the grave, because he-- he was just a piece of ice.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I would say, in my-- in the place where I used to be, which was close to Uchta, the-- the town, not far from Uchta-- U-C-H-T-A-- I would say in my estimation about 40% in that short time, 14 months, died.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all young people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
